title: Concrete Construction Creates Acoustically Sound Units !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
